question: What are the occupations of the Wikipedia authors?
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX dbpedia-ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT ?occupation WHERE { ?person dbpedia-ont:occupation ?occupation . FILTER (EXISTS { ?person rdfs:label ?label . FILTER (regex(?label, 'Wikipedia', 'i')) }) }

question: ¿Cuáles son las ocupaciones de los autores de Wikipedia?
query: PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX ns1: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?occupation WHERE { ?person foaf:page <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wikipedia> . ?person ns1:occupation ?occupation . }

question: Which companies have employed graduates from Stanford University?
query: PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?company WHERE { ?person dbpprop:alumni ?school . ?school dbpprop:name 'Stanford University' . ?person dbpprop:workplace ?company . }

question: ¿Qué empresas han empleado a graduados de la Universidad de Stanford?
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://es.dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?empresa WHERE { ?empresa rdfs:label ?label . FILTER regex(?label, 'empresa|compania|corporacion') . ?graduado dbpedia:alumnoDe dbpedia:Universidad_de_Stanford . ?graduado dbpedia:trabajaEn ?empresa . }

question: Which book has author as J.K. Rowling?
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> ASK WHERE { dbpedia:resource/J.K._Rowling dbpedia-owl:author ?book . }

question: ¿Qué libro tiene como autor a J.K. Rowling?
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?book WHERE { ?book dbpedia-owl:author <http://dbpedia.org/resource/J.K._Rowling> . ?book a dbpedia-owl:Book . }

question: How many books were authored by J.K. Rowling?
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia-ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT COUNT(*) WHERE { ?work dbpedia-ont:author ?author . ?author rdfs:label 'J.K. Rowling'@en . }

question: ¿Cuántos libros fueron escritos por J.K. Rowling?
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX dbpedia-ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT (COUNT(*) AS ?numBooks) WHERE { ?book dbpedia-ont:author <http://dbpedia.org/resource/J.K._Rowling> . ?book a dbpedia-ont:Work . }

question: How many films were recorded by the cinematographer of 'Inception'?
query: PREFIX ns2: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX ns1: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?film) AS ?count) WHERE { ?film ns2:cinematography | ns1:cinematography <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wally_Pfister> . }

question: Is there a university whose campuses are New York and California?
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia-ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT ?university WHERE { ?university a dbpedia-ont:University . ?university dbpedia-ont:location ?location . ?location dbpedia-ont:partOf dbpedia:New_York . ?university dbpedia-ont:location ?location2 . FILTER (regex(str(?location2), 'California')) }

question: Which notable figures are buried in Père Lachaise Cemetery?

question: List all countries, starting with those who have the least amount of universities.
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT ?country (COUNT(?university) AS ?count) WHERE { ?university a dbo:University . ?university dbo:country ?country . ?country a dbo:Country . } GROUP BY ?country ORDER BY ?count

question: Enumere todos los países, comenzando por aquellos que tienen la menor cantidad de universidades.
query: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?country (COUNT(*) AS ?count) WHERE { ?university a dbpedia:University . ?university dbpedia:country ?country . } GROUP BY ?country ORDER BY ?count

question: Which rivers originates from the Rocky Mountains?
